Examples:
  helm create microservices
  helm install my-micro charts/microservices -n demo --create-namespace
  helm upgrade my-micro charts/microservices -n demo
  helm uninstall my-micro -n demo

Repository:
  helm repo add repository_name            Add a new helm repository
  helm repo update                         Update helm repositories
  helm repo remove repository_name         Delete a helm repository
  helm repo ls                             List added repositries

Helm charts management:
  helm install <chart_name>                Install a helm chart
  helm upgrade <chart_name>                Ugprade a helm chart
  helm upgrade --install <chart_name>      Ugprade a helm chart (manage the existing resources instead of creating duplicates)
  helm rollback <chart_name>               Rollback a helm chart
  helm uninstall <release_name>            Uninstall a helm chart

Misc:
  helm list [flags]                        List helm releases in your environment
  helm status <release>                    Get status of a release
  helm search <chart_name>                 Search the available chart using the search command
  helm create <chart_name>                 Create a helm chart
  helm get <chart_release_name>            Download helm chart as a tar archive
  helm dependency update                   Update helm dependencies
